{"componentChunkName":"component---node-modules-antv-gatsby-theme-antv-1-0-3-antv-gatsby-theme-antv-site-templates-document-tsx","path":"/en/docs/specification/language/basic","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"AntV","githubUrl":"https://github.com/antvis","docs":[{"slug":"specification/principles","title":{"zh":"设计原则","en":"Principles"},"order":0},{"slug":"specification/language","title":{"zh":"设计语言","en":"Language"},"order":1},{"slug":"specification/strategy","title":{"zh":"设计策略","en":"Strategies"},"order":2},{"slug":"specification/graph","title":{"zh":"图表设计指引","en":"Visualization Guides"},"order":3},{"slug":"specification/module","title":{"zh":"组件设计指引","en":"Components Guide"},"order":4},{"slug":"specification/module/infoCom","title":{"zh":"信息组件 Info Component","en":"Info Componen"},"order":6},{"slug":"specification/resources","title":{"zh":"资源下载","en":"Resource"},"order":5},{"slug":"specification/tool","title":{"zh":"工具","en":"Tools"},"order":6}]},"pathPrefix":""},"markdownRemark":{"htmlAst":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"AntV 的设计体系中，视觉设计尤为重要。本文主要包括 3 个篇章”布局“、”色板“、”字体“。"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"h2","properties":{"id":"布局","style":"position:relative;"},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"#%E5%B8%83%E5%B1%80","ariaLabel":"布局 permalink","className":["anchor","before"]},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"svg","properties":{"ariaHidden":"true","focusable":"false","height":"16","version":"1.1","viewBox":"0 0 16 16","width":"16"},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"path","properties":{"fillRule":"evenodd","d":"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z"},"children":[]}]}]},{"type":"text","value":"布局"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"有数据表明，人的平均注意力集中时间从 2008 年的 12 秒下降到 2015 年的 8 秒，这个时间还在缩短。我们的大脑每天都要处理海量信息，眼睛会倾向于通过扫视来获取重要信息，扫视的视线流一般是从左至右、从上往下。在数据可视化设计中，布局了决定用户的阅读顺序。在有限的屏幕空间内建立规范的空间布局，可以合理有效地传递信息，让内容为“扫视”而生！"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"h3","properties":{"id":"组件构成","style":"position:relative;"},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"#%E7%BB%84%E4%BB%B6%E6%9E%84%E6%88%90","ariaLabel":"组件构成 permalink","className":["anchor","before"]},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"svg","properties":{"ariaHidden":"true","focusable":"false","height":"16","version":"1.1","viewBox":"0 0 16 16","width":"16"},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"path","properties":{"fillRule":"evenodd","d":"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z"},"children":[]}]}]},{"type":"text","value":"组件构成"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"得益于图形语法的启发，AntV 设计团队从设计角度，将图表进行原子级拆分、抽象，形成这样一套通用组件，如下图中的标题、轴、图形、标签、注解、提示信息、图例等。"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"img","properties":{"src":"https://gw.alipayobjects.com/mdn/rms_a8a5bf/afts/img/A*uYO_TLo_kewAAAAAAAAAAAAAARQnAQ","alt":"image.png"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"h3","properties":{"id":"平面空间布局","style":"position:relative;"},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"#%E5%B9%B3%E9%9D%A2%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E